title: Gelish Candy Land Soak-Off Gel Polish - Sugar N' Spice & Everything Nice
description: Nail Harmony Gelish Candy Land collection.The gel applies like polish but is cured under a UV light like gel nails.Cures in a LED lamp in 30 seconds and in two minutes with 36 watt or higher UV nail light.Gelish stays on nails for three weeks with no chipping or peeling.Soaks completely off in only 15 minutes.

title: Gelish: Color Gels Mini Basix Kit
description: Gelish Mini Basix Kit - This handy BASIX STARTER KIT has mini sizes of Gelish System essentials needed for a Gelish Salon Manicure. (Note: Gelish Soak-Off Gel Polish colors are not included in this kit; they are sold separately) - Includes: pH Bond (9ml/.30 fl oz), Foundation (9ml/.30 fl oz), Top-it-Off (9ml/.30 fl oz), Nourish Cuticle Oil (9ml/.30 fl oz), Nail Surface Cleanse (60ml/2 fl oz), and Artificial Nail Remover (60ml/2 fl oz).
